Title: Pramsh Neem Powder 100gm(100 g)
Description: Alternative Anti-Aging Products with neem oil offer an alternative to synthetic anti-aging products, as the carotenoid content of neem lends it potentially protective qualities; according to a 2009 study published in “Toxicology and Industrial Health,” beta-carotene shields the skin against oxidative stress and ultraviolet radiation, helping reduce the signs of skin aging. Neem oil also contains vitamin C, a natural part of the skin's dermis and epidermis that features antioxidant properties and encourages collagen production. Like cartenoids, vitamin C helps prevent photodamage to the skin. Additionally, the fatty acids of neem oil serve as a moisturizer. Antiseptics for Acne Neem oil features antiseptic properties, which may help those suffering from acne. The plant contains quercetin, an antibacterial and anti-inflammatory flavonoid. Antibacterial agents help reduce acne in some cases, as pimples form due to the occurrence of bacteria in clogged follicles, which contributes to the creation of inflamed red pustules. Quercetin also serves as an antioxidant, which helps reduce membrane-damaging free radicals. Redness Reduction Just as quercetin may help reduce redness, neem oil features other anti-inflammatory components. Neem tree seeds, which produce neem oil, contain 28 liminoids -- chiefly nimbin and its derivatives. As reported by a 2009 study in the “Journal of Oleo Science,” these liminoids exhibit marked anti-inflammatory properties with almost no toxicity. Littmann Select Tunable Diaphragm Stethoscope(Black)
Description: The 3M™ Littmann® Select Stethoscope is a dependable clinical tool for taking blood pressure readings and performing limited physical assessments. It delivers reliable sound quality and the portable convenience of a single-sided chestpiece at an affordable price.Tunable diaphragm technology—a 3M invention—lets medical professionals hear different frequency sounds by simply adjusting the pressure on the chestpiece. Unlike two-sided models, there’s no need to turn over and reposition the chestpiece. Hold the chestpiece with light pressure to hear low frequency sounds; press a little more to hear higher frequency sounds. This time-saving feature allows the healthcare provider to focus on the patient, while the non-chill rim provides patient comfort.Headset tension is easily adjusted for head size and comfort by squeezing together or pulling apart the eartubes. Snap-tight, soft-sealing eartips conform to individual ears for an excellent acoustic seal and comfortable fit. Eartips snap firmly onto the ends of the eartubes and, for safety, require a significant effort to remove.Resilient next-generation tubing retains its shape and flexibility even after folding tightly into a pocket. It provides longer stethoscope life due to improved resistance to skin oils and alcohol, and is less likely to pick up stains. Next-generation tubing is not made with natural rubber latex, a benefit to sensitive medical professionals and their patients. And, to play its part in the protection of human health and the environment, the next-generation tubing does not contain phthalate plasticizers.The Select stethoscope is made in the USA for consistent quality. It comes complete with large soft-sealing ear-tips and instructions.Wide diameter aerospace alloy / Anodized aluminum‎.
